    "description": "Glimmerwick大陆以其魔法大学而闻名 - 幸运的是，你已经被录取了！在这处林地幻想世界中，演奏音乐是施法的秘诀。古老的歌曲使花园工作变得轻而易举，它们亦是探索岛屿各个角落的关键。在这款平和并具有故事情节的角色扮演游戏中，伴随着值得信赖的长笛和歌本，你将上课并参加课外俱乐部、与同学和市民交朋友，并揭露Glimmerwick的诸多怪事和奥秘 - 在一年的季节、节日、咒语和巫师狂欢中愉快畅玩。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色内容</h2><br><strong>角色扮演风格任务</strong><br>关注独特的角色和故事，展开叙事任务。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/6364e9233a0a0553abe851ac09c02645.poster.avif?t=1772167067\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/6364e9233a0a0553abe851ac09c02645.webm?t=1772167067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/6364e9233a0a0553abe851ac09c02645.mp4?t=1772167067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>照料大学花园</strong><br>播种凡间！培育奥术！召唤云彩将雨带来！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/45f0782b45599dd31b11eba97b5d10b2.avif?t=1772167067\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><br><strong>每首歌都具有魔力</strong><br>使用音乐的力量与树木对话，向工具施法使其能自行工作，举起地面来克服天然绝境等等！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/700accd7d81b01121018a06a3e589e71.poster.avif?t=1772167067\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/700accd7d81b01121018a06a3e589e71.webm?t=1772167067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/700accd7d81b01121018a06a3e589e71.mp4?t=1772167067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>生气勃勃的世界</strong><br>上课、神秘谣传、地方戏剧和热闹的节日 — Glimmerwick的学生、员工、市民和精灵生物拥有丰富的故事和生活。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/448d4a26b466994cfe86557ebe77f397.poster.avif?t=1772167067\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/448d4a26b466994cfe86557ebe77f397.webm?t=1772167067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/448d4a26b466994cfe86557ebe77f397.mp4?t=1772167067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>全部有声</strong><br>每位主要角色和次要角色的精彩表演都对话变得栩栩如生。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/f3322bd75100c2420a8ccaadc0ec0fde.avif?t=1772167067\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><br><strong>角色发展</strong><br>当你在冒险中获得经验时，可以选择有助于园艺、交易或获得特殊能力的技能，例如与青蛙说话！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/521fe0b5c7430fc3b8405c38fdbfa842.avif?t=1772167067\" width=500 height=280 /></span><br><br><strong>可定制外观</strong><br>选择你的样貌。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/4d01b9365018aa7728df0a012a8fadb1.poster.avif?t=1772167067\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/4d01b9365018aa7728df0a012a8fadb1.webm?t=1772167067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/4d01b9365018aa7728df0a012a8fadb1.mp4?t=1772167067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>课外活动</strong><br>在Glimmerwick有诸多课外活动 - 探索岛屿、参加飞蛾竞速队、潜水寻找贝壳，或加入绿色精灵参加森林探险。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1706510/extras/5220b1c4945ce0dd852c08552b7667a1.avif?t=1772167067\" width=500 height=280 /></span>",
